
'''= "an industrial alliance dedicated to securing a sustainable supply of raw materials in Europe".'''

URL = https://erma.eu/

=Description=

"The 2020 Communication on Critical Raw Materials announces the launch of an industrial alliance dedicated to securing a sustainable supply of raw materials in Europe. By bringing together all relevant stakeholders along strategic value chains and industrial ecosystems, the alliance will initially focus on the most pressing needs, namely to increase EU resilience in the rare earth elements and permanent magnet value chains. This is vital to key EU industrial ecosystems, such as automotive, renewable energy, defence and aerospace. Later, the alliance will expand to address other critical raw material and base metal needs, including projects supporting the circular economy and addressing the EU Green Deal. There will be an industry-driven process led by EIT RawMaterials, whose task will be to identify opportunities, barriers and create relevant investment cases with stakeholders and industry partners. EIT RawMaterials will publish details of how to join the alliance."
(https://erma.eu/)

